        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer49201251" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16211491523942284460">I adored this novel! It contained all the elements of my favorite contemporary fiction: impeccable historical research, geographic locales that are as strong as the characters, characters who are multi-dimensional &amp; believable, a plot that weaves multiple threads and themes in good pace and with precision. With this, Brooks moves into my favorite authors column. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


